* , a U.S. Navy shipname referring to Benjamin Franklin;
* , an aircraft carrier;
* , a U.S. Coast Guard Point-class cutter;
* , a British Royal Navy third-rate originally built in France as &quot;Franklin&quot;, before being captured at the Battle of the Nile and renamed;
