<doc id="230056" wikidata="Q1535157" url="?curid=230056" title="2nd Golden Raspberry Awards">
<text>The 2nd Golden Raspberry Awards were held on March 29, 1982, at an Oscar night potluck party to recognize the worst the film industry had to offer in 1981.

James Coco, nominated for worst supporting actor for his performance in &quot;Only When I Laugh&quot;, also received a nomination for the Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor for the same performance, a feat not repeated until double supporting actress nominee Amy Irving in 1984.

